      • searchTagTypes

        public TagTypeSearchResponse searchTagTypes(TagTypeSearchRequest request,
                                            Set<String> fields)
        Description copied from interface: TagTypeService
        Retrieves all tag types existing in the system. For each tag type entity, the endpoint returns tag type key by default along with any other top-level elements as specified by the "fields" query string parameter. The list of tag types returned by the endpoint is sorted alphabetically by tag type's order value ascending.
        Specified by:
        searchTagTypes in interface TagTypeService
        Parameters:
        request - the tag type search request. The request does not take any search keys or filters
        fields - the field options for the tag type search response
        Returns:
        the tag type search response
